Privacy Policy for Flirty

Last Updated: [12/19/2023]

Flirty is a dating application designed to connect individuals and foster meaningful relationships. We are committed to ensuring the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how Flirty handles user information.

1. No User Data Collection:

Flirty does not collect any personal information from its users. We do not gather data such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other personally identifiable information.

2. Location Information:

Flirty may request access to your device's location services to enhance the user experience. However, this information is used solely within the app for location-based features and is not stored or shared with third parties.

3. Information Security:

While Flirty may use certain device permissions for functionality, no user data is stored or transmitted outside of the app. Your data security is our priority.

4. Third-Party Services:

Flirty may integrate third-party services for enhanced features. Users are encouraged to review the privacy policies of these third-party services, as they may have separate data collection practices.

5. Changes to Privacy Policy:

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Users will be notified of any significant changes, and the updated policy will be posted on our website.

6. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or Flirty's data practices, please contact us at yahya.ali.barki@gmail.com.

By using Flirty, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
